= Action name = PCK.AUTOMIC_SONIC.PUB.ACTION.ADD_VLAN
= General description = This action will Add a VLAN on sonic.
=Setup= * For SSH, Enable SSH on the target system.
= Inputs = - VLAN ID* : Provide ID of the VLAN to be added. E.g. 100
= Failure Conditions = If the user provides invalid VLAN ID e.g non numeric. If user will not provide sudo credentials properly.
=Return Value= (none)
= Logging = Logs will be displayed in the AE report.
= Example = * VLAN ID : 100 ----------------------------------------------
